name: trInkdBer
description:
When I was in a prompt competition last year, I got a ver good sequence to get beautiful illustrations. My prompt is lost, so I create this embedding. If you wanna test it, you can put this word on the prompt: trInkdBer .

PS: The test images was made with 'vainilla' SD 1.5 model. I don't know if works on SD 2.1 .
